subject: Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: The reserve Andre Dawkins scored 22 points and the freshman Austin Rivers added 20 to lead No. 5 Duke to a 74-66 victory over No. 15 Florida State on Thursday night in Gainesville, Fla.
